import React from 'react';
import {
  MDBContainer,
  MDBRow,
  MDBCol,
  MDBCard,
  MDBCardBody,
  MDBCardTitle,
  MDBCardText,
  MDBCardImage,
  MDBBtn
} from 'mdb-react-ui-kit';

const CardRow = () => {
  return (
    <MDBContainer>
      <MDBRow>
        <MDBCol md='2'>
          <MDBCard style={{ maxWidth: '18rem' }}>
            <MDBCardImage src='https://mdbootstrap.com/img/new/standard/nature/184.webp' position='top' alt='...' />
            <MDBCardBody>
              <MDBCardTitle>Card 1</MDBCardTitle>
              <MDBCardText>Some quick example text for card 1.</MDBCardText>
              <MDBBtn href='#'>Button</MDBBtn>
            </MDBCardBody>
          </MDBCard>
        </MDBCol>

        <MDBCol md='2'>
          <MDBCard style={{ maxWidth: '18rem' }}>
            <MDBCardImage src='https://mdbootstrap.com/img/new/standard/nature/184.webp' position='top' alt='...' />
            <MDBCardBody>
              <MDBCardTitle>Card 2</MDBCardTitle>
              <MDBCardText>Some quick example text for card 2.</MDBCardText>
              <MDBBtn href='#'>Button</MDBBtn>
            </MDBCardBody>
          </MDBCard>
        </MDBCol>

        <MDBCol md='2'>
          <MDBCard style={{ maxWidth: '18rem' }}>
            <MDBCardImage src='https://mdbootstrap.com/img/new/standard/nature/184.webp' position='top' alt='...' />
            <MDBCardBody>
              <MDBCardTitle>Card 3</MDBCardTitle>
              <MDBCardText>Some quick example text for card 3.</MDBCardText>
              <MDBBtn href='#'>Button</MDBBtn>
            </MDBCardBody>
          </MDBCard>
        </MDBCol>
      </MDBRow>
    </MDBContainer>
  );
};

export default CardRow;
